Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.service.fluent

Class NavigationServiceFluent<T extends UiServiceFluent<?>>

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.service.fluent.NavigationServiceFluent<T>
public class NavigationServiceFluent<T extends UiServiceFluent<?>> extends Object
A fluent service class for handling navigation-related actions in a web automation framework.

Provides methods to navigate between pages, handle browser tabs/windows, interact with frames, and manage alerts.

The generic type T represents the UI service fluent implementation that extends UiServiceFluent, allowing method chaining for seamless interaction.
